{"tid":2132740,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Hong Kong Fishballs - 一個簡單的遊戲，記錄了香港小販文化","createTime":"2020-07-30T14:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T14:19:05.000Z","uid":321748,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e552c8ef20a09dd96ae055eb255b481f01ee5704","tid":2132740,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:19:05.000Z","msg":"&quot;Hong Kong Fishballs&quot; (2016)<br />\n<br />\n在這個遊戲裡﹐你化身成小販﹐在香港賣魚蛋這種用魚漿製作的著名本地街頭食品。魚蛋賣得越多越好﹐直到小販管理隊出現。這個時候，你要想的，就只是這一廣東話字詞：「走鬼」──逃跑，要不然被捉著的話，就會被罰款及沒收小販車。逃跑不易的，因為你需要在狹窄、擁擠和淩亂的香港街道左閃右避。幸運的話，一天辛苦掙來的錢就真正可以用來養家糊口，這是部分香港草根市民出來當小販的原因。<br />\n<br />\n一個簡單的遊戲，就帶出了不少香港地道文化。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲連結: <a href=\"https://pokedev8.itch.io/fishballs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokedev8.itch.io%2Ffishballs&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=7c5eb2bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pokedev8.itch.io/fishballs</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-E5IKArNNqqU/XyLT3MZ8MwI/AAAAAAAAHwE/Cr8zHfOQ4lA0wrQKf2PC8wuIe3sfukaDQCLcBGAsYHQ/s640/HawkerLifecycle.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-E5IKArNNqqU%2FXyLT3MZ8MwI%2FAAAAAAAAHwE%2FCr8zHfOQ4lA0wrQKf2PC8wuIe3sfukaDQCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs640%2FHawkerLifecycle.png&h=4133f2a1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}